<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


知乎用户，<strong title="那个啥，知识不一定是性感，但是性感一定要有姿势U_U" class="zu-question-my-bio">那个啥，知识不一定是性感，但是性感一定…</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="6">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$yu-zhou-zhuan-ye-zha-zhi-ji" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/yu-zhou-zhuan-ye-zha-zhi-ji" class="zg-link" title="宇宙专业榨汁机">宇宙专业榨汁机</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$li-ji-di-61" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/li-ji-di-61" class="zg-link" title="李济迪">李济迪</a></span>
